// <Name>Coverage regression on methods 100% covered by tests</Name>
WARN IF Count > 0 IN SELECT METHODS WHERE 
HasAttribute "OPTIONAL:NDepend.CQL.FullCoveredAttribute" AND PercentageCoverage < 100

// NDepend.CQL.FullCoveredAttribute is defined in the redistributable assembly $NDependInstallDir$\Lib\NDepend.CQL.dll
// You can define your own attribute to tag '100% covered' methods.

// To run this constraint properly coverage data must be gathered from NCover™ or Visual Studio™ Coverage.
// This can be done in VisualNDepend throught the menu: Coverage -> Import Coverage Files
// This can be done at analysis time throught the menu: Project Properties -> Analysis -> Code Coverage
